## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="1af34-114">Le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructeur initialise le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> propriété.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af34-114">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor initializes the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Id%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1af34-115">L’identificateur doit être unique au sein d’une grammaire donnée.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af34-115">The identifier must be unique within a given grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="1af34-116">Le <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructeur lève une <xref:System.FormatException> dans les circonstances suivantes :</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1af34-116">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A> constructor throws a <xref:System.FormatException> in the following circumstances:</span></span>  
  
